 To search for courses, select one of the links below to view a list of courses by term in a PDF file that is updated daily. You can download a free copy of Acrobat Reader from http://get.adobe.com/reader. UNT All Classes UNT Core Classes UNT Honors Classes College of Arts and Sciences College of Business College of Education College of Engineering Honors College College of Information Mayborn School of Journalism College of Merchandising, Hospitality and Tourism College of Music College of Health and Public Service College of Visual Arts and Design Contact Information Office of the RegistrarEagle Student Services Building, Room 1471155 Union Circle #311400 Denton TX, 76203　 Office: (940) 565-2378 E-mail:registrar@unt.eduWeb:registrar.unt.edu Additional Resources Registrar Website How to View Online Courses Offered Student Services Registration Guides Visit Us Chilton Hall 410 Avenue C Office Suite 112 Denton, TX 76203 USA Mail Us Center for Learning Enhancement, Assessment, and Redesign (CLEAR) 1155 Union Circle #310889 Denton, Texas 76203-5017 Contact Us 940-565-2708 online@unt.edu Technical issues? Site last updated on May 04, 2017 Disclaimer| AA/EOE/ADA| Privacy| Electronic Accessibility| State of Texas Online| Emergency Preparedness| THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information| UNT Compliance Hotline| Governors Committee on People with Disabilities| Texas Veterans Portal| UNT Home Site last updated on May 04, 2017 | Important Links 